<span id="freeTextContainer16273203975922348101">I really don’t like Paulo Coelho’s books, at least not the ones I read. <br/>While he obviously has a good writing style, his writing is too didactic/moralistic. It’s like he is a teacher who wants his students to understand a point and writes a book to explain it. Some people might like it, but for me there really is too little interesting to like.</span>

